snippet.title: Super Paper Bowser World NCFC 2011 Trailer
snippet.description: Super Paper Bowser World is back! Yeah! Coming this Winter, bigger, badder and better than ever! Check the NCFC booth, and the MFGG or BibbyTeam topic for more info. YouTube sucks the quality down, btw :(
